{"tid":1400760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「小心個頭」驚賊又用煙幕","createTime":"2019-08-03T13:44:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T13:46:57.000Z","uid":263806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0db25a750198b9f2b8de1957fc01ec0dcd145937","tid":1400760,"uid":263806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:44:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EwXienT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEwXienT.png&h=4953b3f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上次中上西環都係咁<br />\n等記者咩證據都影唔到<br />\n<br />\n然 後 HEADSHOT<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yddxiQp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyddxiQp.png&h=296e4fd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n［人多時］見到畜龍唔好跑走<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379843\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379843</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我無野講了<br />\n我唔支持今日守到咁夜<br />\n所以我無出席<br />\n<br />\n岩岩望住直播又一千人見到畜龍就跑走<br />\n上次個個戰後都好同意下次多人就會圍<br />\n<br />\n又捉咗幾個了<br />\n<br />\n我今次真係無野好講"},{"pid":"72b00f74c46e4e119f6e3f8dfcbe9fd7f2818123","tid":1400760,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:44:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不分化<br />\n明白大家唔同意見<br />\n呢篇野原意唔係反港獨<br />\n而係希望大家集中翻五大訴求</span></span><br />\n港獨？小心啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400357\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0a1c0092f6038a61680eceda9aa2194dfb4a97d8","tid":1400760,"uid":263806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:46:28.000Z","msg":"跑走=害死最前排前線"},{"pid":"57e8bc68a74854c2e683039ded17d589f8c33542","tid":1400760,"uid":263806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:46:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚攰"}]}